@@TJvExMaskEdit.ClipboardCommands
Summary
  Specifies the clipboard commands that are enabled for the control.
Description
  Use ClipboardCommands to specify which clipboard commands are allowed for the edit control.
  
  * ClipboardCommands can't be set to [].
  * If ClipboardCommands is set to [caCopy] then property ReadOnly is set to True.

